{"tid":611559,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿諾舒華辛力加心臟手術後情況穩定醒來第一句：I'm back","createTime":"2018-03-31T06:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T12:21:49.000Z","uid":105567,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab4035f1cfa3ffd904fc5b81dd6151c9bfa019e0","tid":611559,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/173631/阿諾舒華辛力加心臟手術後情況穩定-醒來第一句-我回來了\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F173631%2F%E9%98%BF%E8%AB%BE%E8%88%92%E8%8F%AF%E8%BE%9B%E5%8A%9B%E5%8A%A0%E5%BF%83%E8%87%9F%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%BE%8C%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A-%E9%86%92%E4%BE%86%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%A5-%E6%88%91%E5%9B%9E%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86&d=dpqLdsyiDwYmAhPdvKDemjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=eadbbdf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/173631/阿諾舒華辛力加心臟手術後情況穩定-醒來第一句-我回來了</a><br />\n<br />\n美國加州前州長、荷里活影星阿諾舒華辛力加（Arnold Schwarzenegger），周四（29日）在美國洛杉磯一家醫院進行更換導管主動脈瓣手術，目前情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n70歲的阿諾舒華辛力加由於有先天心臟缺陷，曾在1997年植入導管活瓣，今次手術是要更換有關活瓣。這次原本只是一次微創手術，但由於出現併發症，醫院須為阿諾舒華辛力加進行數小時的緊急心臟手術。<br />\n<br />\n他的發言人凱切爾（Daniel Ketchell）指，阿諾手術後精神良好，又引用他在電影《未來戰士》（Terminator）經典對白，指自己「回來了」。 <br />\n<br />\n生於奧地利的阿諾舒華辛力加憑代表作《未來戰士》在荷李活影壇走紅，但他起初是一名健美運動員，自15歲開始健身，曾贏得世界健美先生榮譽，又曾於2003年至2011年擔任加州州長，卸任後在政壇仍然活躍，曾批評總統特朗普（Donald Trump）。"},{"pid":"57b3e55c6e71112c16c4b97e63a47c7a7b659d25","tid":611559,"uid":146493,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:35:41.000Z","msg":"拍戲拍到傻撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6af0f5e98a778e645d9e6c7861f80b550d66cc","tid":611559,"uid":65144,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍戲拍到傻撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人真係冇幽默感多認真撚，人地冇事出返黎開句玩笑都比支那香港人串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed133f20be5d49453eda53e910a941dc6f068b0","tid":611559,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:33:19.000Z","msg":"以為係follow me<br />\nbtw,支那01"},{"pid":"c95f4e55ac193e1d694635db4a521ab1ea06ff96","tid":611559,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/4TAab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2F4TAab.jpg&h=c3f3240c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/4TWW6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2F4TWW6.jpg&h=650491c7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}